caption:
Poached eggs à la casino parking lot. Where’s the weirdest place you’ve made breakfast?

The last 7+ years living on the road we’ve realized how much we’ve enjoyed staying in casino parking lots. They always have security, usually pretty level parking, lots of food and beverage options, and the nights are quiet. This particular one even has a dump and water fill so we can easily shower and fill/empty our tanks when needed.
